    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对一台完美而不朽的机器，你将如何应战？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nightdive Studios 倾力打造的经典第一人称射击游戏/角色扮演游戏重制版——《System Shock® 2: 25th Anniversary Remaster》——将为您带来跨平台联机合作、模组支持等崭新体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/866570/extras/cd43e93a6754e91d23c0cd112a07b753.poster.avif?t=1769786955\" width=626 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/866570/extras/cd43e93a6754e91d23c0cd112a07b753.webm?t=1769786955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/866570/extras/cd43e93a6754e91d23c0cd112a07b753.mp4?t=1769786955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2114 年，当你从冯·布劳恩号超光速飞船的冷冻舱中苏醒时，你不仅记忆全失，而且不知自己身在何处。而眼前的一切已陷入恐怖境地：变异生物与杀戮机器人在船舱中四处游荡，而幸存船员的惨叫声则在冰冷的船体中不断回响。叛变的人工智能 SHODAN 正图谋毁灭人类，而阻止这场浩劫的重任，已落在你的肩上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/866570/extras/4bfdd3f95d3ce11dcaccf0578db91bf4.poster.avif?t=1769786955\" width=626 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/866570/extras/4bfdd3f95d3ce11dcaccf0578db91bf4.webm?t=1769786955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/866570/extras/4bfdd3f95d3ce11dcaccf0578db91bf4.mp4?t=1769786955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这艘荒废的冯·布劳恩号上，你将逐层探索每一处舱室，揭开这艘飞船及其船员背后的骇人真相。扣人心弦的剧情与精心打造的场景将为你呈现一场沉浸感十足的太空冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《System Shock® 2: 25th Anniversary Remaster》的核心特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持跨平台联机合作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特工局、陆战队、海军部三大兵种任你选择，尽享独特作战风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强化的模组支持系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持超宽屏与 144 高帧率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 个奖杯待你解锁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全面升级的角色、武器模型与动画效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完善的手柄支持。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多项游戏体验优化升级。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
